00:32:02,207 --> 00:32:05,904
Packed neatly in four cases
with an inventory.

481
00:32:05,977 --> 00:32:08,639
Alas...no note.

482
00:32:10,281 --> 00:32:13,910
I'll send someone over
to pick them up.

483
00:32:13,985 --> 00:32:15,612
Thank you for your help.

484
00:32:26,097 --> 00:32:28,122
Thanks.

485
00:32:29,701 --> 00:32:31,828
How's it goin'? Any leads?

486
00:32:31,903 --> 00:32:34,895
