and public shaming.

497
00:33:53,017 --> 00:33:54,917
My own never bothered me...

498
00:33:54,986 --> 00:33:58,251
except for the inconvenience
of being incarcerated.

499
00:33:58,323 --> 00:34:01,656
But you may lack perspective.

500
00:34:01,726 --> 00:34:03,990
In our discussions
down in the dungeon...

501
00:34:04,062 --> 00:34:06,462
it was apparent to me
that your father...

502
00:34:06,531 --> 00:34:08,055
the dead night watchman...

503
00:34:08,132 --> 00:34:11,295
figures largely
in your value system.

504
00:34:11,369 --> 00:34:13,997
I think your success
