of a promising career?

513
00:34:36,527 --> 00:34:39,963
What is worst about
this humiliation, Clarice?

514
00:34:40,031 --> 00:34:41,328
Is it how your failure...

515
00:34:41,399 --> 00:34:44,027
will reflect
on your mommy and daddy?

516
00:34:45,370 --> 00:34:47,838
Is your worst fear that people
will now and forever...

517
00:34:47,905 --> 00:34:49,566
believe they were indeed...

518
00:34:49,640 --> 00:34:53,337
just good old trailer camp,
tornado-bait, white trash?

519
00:34:53,411 --> 00:34:57,677
And that perhaps you are, too?

520
00:34:59,150 --> 00:35:00,549
By the way,
I couldn't help noticing...

521
00:35:00,618 --> 00:35:02,882
on the FBl's
rather dull public website...

522
00:35:02,954 --> 00:35:04,512
that I have been hoisted...

523
00:35:04,589 --> 00:35:07,183
from the Bureau's archives
of the common criminal...

524
00:35:07,258 --> 00:35:09,192
and elevated
to the more prestigious...

525
00:35:09,260 --> 00:35:11,694
Ten Most Wanted List.

526
00:35:11,763 --> 00:35:16,097
Is this coincidence,
