Special Agent Starling.

533
00:35:37,755 --> 00:35:42,624
Regards, your old pal,
Hannibal Lecter, M.D.

534
00:35:44,128 --> 00:35:45,322
P.S.

535
00:35:45,396 --> 00:35:48,695
