part of the bargain...

537
00:35:50,735 --> 00:35:53,568
but you accepted it, Clarice.

538
00:35:53,638 --> 00:35:56,266
Your job is to craft my doom.

539
00:35:56,340 --> 00:35:59,070
So I am not sure how well
I should wish you...

540
00:35:59,143 --> 00:36:01,634
but I'm sure
we'll have a lot of fun.

541
00:36:01,712 --> 00:36:04,306
Ta-ta. "H."

542
00:36:11,589 --> 00:36:13,056
On the letter...

