All right, then, tell me how.

562
00:37:08,946 --> 00:37:12,438
No. It's your turn
to tell me, Clarice.

563
00:37:12,517 --> 00:37:16,954
You have no more vacations
to sell on Anthrax lsland.

564
00:37:17,021 --> 00:37:19,012
Quid pro quo, Clarice.

565
00:37:19,090 --> 00:37:22,059
I tell you things,
you tell me things.

566
00:37:22,126 --> 00:37:25,527
Not about this case.
About yourself.

567
00:37:25,596 --> 00:37:27,086
Quid pro quo.

568
00:37:27,165 --> 00:37:30,225
