569
00:37:41,412 --> 00:37:43,243
Hand cream.

570
00:37:45,249 --> 00:37:47,843
Raw ambergris base.

571
00:37:49,153 --> 00:37:51,587
Tennessee lavender.

572
00:37:52,657 --> 00:37:55,091
Trace of something else.

573
00:37:56,694 --> 00:37:57,854
Fleece.

574
00:37:57,929 --> 00:38:00,557
