on every 3-0-2, understand?

655
00:45:51,602 --> 00:45:53,797
If you work with me...

656
00:45:53,871 --> 00:45:56,669
then your so-called career here
might improve.

657
00:45:58,475 --> 00:46:02,741
If you don't,
then all I have to do...

658
00:46:02,813 --> 00:46:06,249
is draw a line through your name
rather than under it...

659
00:46:06,316 --> 00:46:07,681
and it's over.

660
00:46:07,751 --> 00:46:10,219
Paul, what is it with you?

661
00:46:10,287 --> 00:46:13,415
I told you to go home
to your wife. That was wrong?

662
00:46:13,490 --> 00:46:16,687
Don't flatter yourself,
Starling.

663
00:46:16,760 --> 00:46:19,558
That was a long time ago.

664
00:46:19,630 --> 00:46:23,691
Why would I hold that
against you?

665
00:46:23,767 --> 00:46:28,727
And besides, this town is full
of corn-pone country pussy.

666
00:46:30,274 --> 00:46:33,573
That said, I wouldn't mind
having a go with you now...

667
00:46:33,644 --> 00:46:35,373
if you want to reconsider.

668
00:46:35,446 --> 00:46:37,676
In the gym, anytime.

669
00:46:37,748 --> 00:46:38,908
No pads.

670
00:46:43,253 --> 00:46:46,017
Is it possible it went out
with the regular mail?

671
00:46:46,090 --> 00:46:49,992
No, I overnighted it to you.
I filled out the slip myself.

672
00:46:50,060 --> 00:46:52,221
This was the day
after your request.

673
00:46:52,296 --> 00:46:53,923
I did it right away.

674
00:46:53,997 --> 00:46:55,589
I don't understand
what happened.

675
00:46:55,666 --> 00:46:57,224
You should have it by now.

676
00:46:57,301 --> 00:46:59,462
I don't.
Can you send me another one?

677
00:46:59,536 --> 00:47:02,300
Sure. I will make another copy
especially for you...

678
00:47:02,372 --> 00:47:04,169
Agent...Clarice?

679
00:47:04,241 --> 00:47:06,209
Is that right?
Can I call you Clarice?

680
00:47:06,276 --> 00:47:07,607
Agent Starling.

681
00:47:07,678 --> 00:47:09,202
I'd appreciate it.

682
00:47:09,279 --> 00:47:10,405
