683
00:47:10,481 --> 00:47:13,450
My name is Franco Benetti.
Agent Franco Benetti.

684
00:47:13,517 --> 00:47:15,815
Thank you very much,
Agent Benetti.

685
00:47:16,887 --> 00:47:19,447
-I'll send you tomorrow?
-All right.

686
00:47:22,292 --> 00:47:23,691
Nothin', huh?

687
00:47:23,761 --> 00:47:25,160
Nothin' yet.

688
00:47:25,229 --> 00:47:26,992
Still waitin' on
Florence and London.

689
00:48:03,534 --> 00:48:07,561
The number you have dialed
is not in service at this time.

690
00:48:07,638 --> 00:48:09,105
Please check the numb--

691
00:48:35,265 --> 00:48:37,825
I have information
about Hannibal Lecter.

692
00:48:37,901 --> 00:48:41,268
Have you shared your information
with the police, sir?

693
00:48:41,338 --> 00:48:43,704
I'm required to encourage you
to do so.

694
00:48:45,676 --> 00:48:49,942
Is the reward payable
under special circumstances?

695
00:48:50,013 --> 00:48:52,504
May I suggest
you contact an attorney...

696
00:48:52,583 --> 00:48:55,108
