any possibly illegal action?

697
00:48:55,185 --> 00:48:58,382
There's one in Geneva who is
excellent in these matters.

698
00:48:58,455 --> 00:49:00,446
May I give you
his toll-free number?

699
00:49:00,524 --> 00:49:06,554
The number is
0-0-4-1-2-3-3-1-7.

700
00:49:06,630 --> 00:49:08,359
Thank you for calling.

701
00:49:29,152 --> 00:49:30,585
